description.en: SafeCoin leverages the most advanced safety and privacy based cryptocurrency technology available today. The project is rapidly implementing new features to make the currency more practical and user-friendly; whilst working to continually discover improvements in cryptocurrency privacy, safety, and security. SafeCoin was launch in early 2018 with a small pre-mine of four million coins and a max supply of 36 million coins. SafeCoin was launched with the Equihash algorithm, though the team are exploring other ASIC resistance options. SafeCoin was designed with security and privacy in mind.

status_updates.description:
New world record set in blockchain energy efficiency

New standards have been set in energy efficiency following successful benchmarking in mainnet for Safecoin, a community focused Defi system and blockchain built on enhanced Solana blockchain technology.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBpp5ri_39M

An AMA will be held to provide more information on this benchmarking as well as other developments in Safecoin:

https://www.safecoin.org/events/safecoin-ama-july-24th-2022/

Safebridge is going live

This is an essential AMA for any Defi project to attend that is looking for greater resiliency, adoption, and community for their tokens, smart contracts, and dApps.   Learn how any Solana or Ethereum project (more coming) can decentralize though Safebridge to mitigate downtime and congestion, while reaching wider audiences and new markets.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E8sT9zC2kdM&list=TLGGjWnhElp44UUwMjA1MjAyMg

We will be holding a Q4 AMA this Sunday, October 3rd at 6 PM UTC to discuss our project status and direction.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FAXtfenbR5o

We are pleased to announce our support of a 1:1 SAFE backed ERC-20 token, with a supply of 360,000 ( 1% of total SafeCoin supply.

https://etherscan.io/token/0xdAF566020156297E2837fDfaA6Fbba929A29461E


SafeTrade holds custody of and responsibility for this 1:1 backed token, with collateral SafeCoin held at:

 https://explorer.safecoin.org/address/AzAGXGLroqnD4dQDK962cVaxTSaX53GuthyFM86GFaWN

https://safe.trade/trading/esafesafe

We are extremely excited to proceed with our launch of Safecoin Validators today!
Upon completion of Safecoin Validators, our attention turns to DeFi applications, as the launch of SafeSwap and other anticipated platforms approaches.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nFy88YQv1bU

Going Live in 20 Minutes ( 6pm UTC)
Hope to see you there!

We are pleased to present Safecoin Validators in an AMA format, a significant advancement in crypto for performance in community based projects, based on Solana Technology.   We've worked hard to keep all of the incredible Solana features while making these validators feasible for our community, forming the foundation upon which Safecoin will provide on chain solutions for individuals, governments, and businesses

LIVE NOW: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mfCe8dLEfRc

* 37 DAYS REMAINING TO SWAP *

LIVE AMA this Sunday for information regarding Safecoin Validators - setup and hardware requirements, swap status, staking - everything you wanted to know and more!

Please Join us on Sunday April 4th at 18:00 UTC!

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Xlk0kvbB70&feature=youtu.be&ab_channel=Safecoin

Join us on discord also!
https://discord.gg/QXHn2JpK
